  "detailed_description": "For the first time ever, you are able to immerse yourself in a world of milling.<br><br>Use a conventional milling machine to drill, mill, grind and cut.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.poster.avif?t=1772550539\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.webm?t=1772550539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/2915ac24ea2e827f35909b4a9a1fb8e2.mp4?t=1772550539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Import your own blueprints, to prototype unique products in Free milling mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.poster.avif?t=1772550539\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.webm?t=1772550539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/69c47acf0f73ef558a8c7c662cd00535.mp4?t=1772550539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Measure with precision and complete challenging tasks in Career mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/42c83d7b920e790692daabab7bc41beb.poster.avif?t=1772550539\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787960/extras/42c83d7b920e790692daabab7bc41beb.webm?t=1772550539\" ty